These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, november
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Birthday     | november | april  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, go
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Game    | mah-jongg      | go         |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, writer
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the teacher is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Job   | writer | teacher   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, indonesian
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, dressmaker
1. the indonesian is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | french  | indonesian |
| Job         | journalist | dressmaker    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
