The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Cigar      | oliveros | baccarat |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | crime  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
